title: Episode 27 - Steven Bradbury Interview (Brink Vault 2009)
itunes:title: Episode 27 - Steven Bradbury Interview (Brink Vault 2009)
description: Another 'vault' interview from our parent show The Brink today as we chat with the first ever Winter Olympic Gold Medalist from Australia, Steven Bradbury. In this 2009 chat, Steven takes us through is career as well as going over that iconic moment from Salt Lake City in 2002 which still stands out today as one of the greatest moments in the history of the Olympic Games.
